Package tools.data.collection.rb_tree

Class RBNode<D extends RBKey>

  • java.lang.Object
    • tools.data.collection.rb_tree.RBNode<D>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LinkedRBNode
    public class RBNode<D extends RBKey>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores the information about the node in the RBTree data structure. The value of this node is calculated from the given object.
